Source.Name: diffoscope
Source.Summary: In-depth comparison of files, archives, and directories
Source.Description: diffoscope tries to get to the bottom of what makes files or directories different. It will recursively unpack archives of many kinds and transform various binary formats into more human-readable form to compare them. It can compare two tarballs, ISO images, or PDF just as easily.
